unalias cc-mainevent-command cc-mainevent-engineering cc-mainevent-science cc-mainevent-sickbay cc-mainevent-tactical cc-mainevent-comms cc-mainevent-helm 2>/dev/null
unalias cc-dns-command cc-dns-bugbay cc-dns-testing cc-dns-build cc-dns-refactor cc-dns-apidesign cc-dns-docs 2>/dev/null
